column5: Any info on spots to fish in minnitaki

Where are you staying? Minnataki is a long lake. Where we fish might be 25 mile ride for you. If your staying near Sioux Lookout I can help you out. If your down on the pickerel arm not so much. Leaving Friday, can't wait.
Stayin in sioux lookout lookin for bigger walleyes
When are you headding up? I'm with the walleye wrangler. He always catches the biggest walleyes. He will have a 29 in the boat by Saturday afternoon.
Tony, i sent you a private message. Had a couple of more questions for you.
Heading up for my first time to Canada this friday as well. Can't wait!
i fished minny everyday last week ant the fishing was good above the shutes.
